description:
The investment seeks long-term capital appreciation and the potential for current income, while also seeking to protect principal during unfavorable market conditions.
 The fund will seek to invest in the equity securities of large capitalization domestic and foreign companies that WBI Investments, Inc., the sub-advisor ("Sub-Advisor") to the fund and an affiliate of Millington Securities Inc., the advisor ("Advisor"), believes display an attractive financial condition and prospects for ongoing financial stability, and in other tactical investment opportunities. It may invest up to 50% of its net assets in the securities of issuers in emerging markets.
